.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: spy, family, fantasy, horror, comedy
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, april, november, june, may
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the person watching spy movies is the person who likes red
2. the person watching swedish movies is the owner of the dog
3. the person watching family movies is the person who's birthday is in june
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person who's birthday is in april
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the owner of the bird
7. the person who likes yellow is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person who's birthday is in november is in the middle
9. the person watching horror movies is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's birthday is in august
13. the person watching fantasy movies is the prince-smoker
14. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Movie-Genre	|   horror	|    family	|    spy	|    fantasy	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| Birthday	|    may	|     june	|     november	|    april	|      august	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
